(26, 1, '2014-10-21 15:40:09', '2014-10-21 15:40:09', '<h1>Interested ina career with Bowman Riley?</h1>\r\n<p>At Bowman Riley, we recognise that investment in our people in terms of career development, training, staff satisfaction and a rewarding work environment is critical to the success of our business.</p>\r\n<p>For the fifth consecutive year, Bowman Riley Architects has been selected as one of the top 50 companies to work for in the UKs construction industry by Building magazine as featured in this month''s Good Employer Guide.</p>\r\n<p>If you are interested in joining our growing and talented team, please send a copy of your CV, examples of work and a covering letter using the link below.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Work With Us', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'work-with-us', '', '', '2014-11-04 14:33:01', '2014-11-04 14:33:01', '', 8, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?page_id=26', 5, 'page', '', 0),
