(61, 1, '2014-10-22 08:21:26', '2014-10-22 08:21:26', '<p>After working in Montego Bay, Jamaica, Matthew joined Bowman Riley Architects in 1997. He established the central Leeds office over ten years ago and the London office in 2012. He manages both teams specialising in commercial, retail, residential and industrial projects. Matthew is a keen golfer, former rugby player and enjoys live music.</p>', 'Matthew Jones', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'matthew-jones', '', '', '2014-10-30 09:44:06', '2014-10-30 09:44:06', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=61', 0, 'people', '', 0),
