(446, 1, '2014-10-30 08:21:48', '2014-10-30 08:21:48', '<h3>Assam Clubhouse and Apartments</h3>\n<p>Bowman Riley Architects designed a private members club with 18 hotel rooms and 142 residential apartments in the largest city of Assam in India, the largest metropolitan area in north-eastern India.</p>\n<p>The clubhouse and apartments development sits within the tea growing capital of India and the design draws inspiration from its mountainous location.</p>\n<p>This 200,000ft luxury residential development is comprised of five high specification apartment towers and a private members club.</p>\n<p>The 50,000ft Clubhouse has been designed to the highest specification to give guests the ultimate luxury experience. The facilities includes a health and fitness suite, spa, 5 star hotel, banqueting facilities, roof top pool and revolving restaurant.</p>\n<p>Bowman Riley also designed the interiors for the clubhouse, using the best local materials to provide a truly memorable experience.</p>', 'Private', 'Bowman Riley Architects designed a private members club with 18 hotel rooms and 142 residential apartments in the largest city of Assam in India, the largest metropolitan area in north-eastern India.', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '90-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-10-30 08:21:48', '2014-10-30 08:21:48', '', 90, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/uncategorized/90-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
