(493, 1, '2014-10-30 09:42:07', '2014-10-30 09:42:07', '<h3>Yorkshire Housing Standard House Types</h3>\r\n<p>Yorkshire Housing commissioned Bowman Riley Architects to design their standard house types to include two, three and four bedroom houses, bungalows and apartments.</p>\r\n<p>The standardisation of house types and specifications offers Yorkshire Housing more control in the final outcome of each specific project.</p>\r\n<p>Working closely with our client, we discussed the house types required and collated input from Yorkshire Housings team before producing the final house types.</p>\r\n<p>Our designs are highly regarded by Yorkshire Housing and will be used on all future Yorkshire Housing planning submissions.</p>\r\n<p>On an on-going basis, we will manage the house types to make any changes to meet the evolving needs of our client and their residents.</p>', 'Yorkshire Housing', 'Yorkshire Housing commissioned Bowman Riley Architects to design their standard house types to include two, three and four bedroom houses, bungalows and apartments.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'yorkshire-housing-4', '', '', '2014-10-30 09:42:07', '2014-10-30 09:42:07', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=casestudies&#038;p=493', 0, 'casestudies', '', 0),
