(518, 1, '2014-10-30 11:21:21', '2014-10-30 11:21:21', '<h3>The Ridge Medical Practice</h3>\r\n<p>The Ridge Medical Practices existing premises had become outdated and outgrown. The practice needed a new building to realise their vision of delivering top-quality primary care in a welcoming environment and to broaden the range of services offered. The practice wanted to co-locate other primary care trust community nursing teams in the building to deliver a truly joined-up package to the community.</p>\r\n<p>Steve Batson was appointed as project architect to design the new centre on a one acre site close to the existing location. The site included an old manor house, which was derelict but listed. The development involved the renovation of the manor house and the construction of a new building that had to sit comfortably alongside the listed building.</p>\r\n<p>Integral to our design process was a consideration of sustainability. As well as designing a well-insulated and efficient modern building, we have added many extra features to reduce the impact on the environment including solar panels, natural ventilation systems, under-floor heating, minimal use of air conditioning and a natural sedum roof</p>\r\n<p>The new medical centre comprises 3,000m over four floors, providing 24 consulting rooms, nurse treatment room, two minor surgery rooms, rehabilitation gym, practice administration areas, meeting and training rooms, pharmacy and the space leased to the primary care trust community teams.</p>', 'The Ridge Medical Practice', 'The Ridge Medical Practices existing premises had become outdated and outgrown. ', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ridge-medical-practice', '', '', '2014-10-30 11:21:21', '2014-10-30 11:21:21', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=casestudies&#038;p=518', 0, 'casestudies', '', 0),
(519, 1, '2014-10-30 11:23:04', '2014-10-30 11:23:04', '<h3>Thorpe Park Clinic</h3>\r\n<p>Living Care Group opened a third centre in the Yorkshire region to host a mix of NHS outpatient clinics, extensive diagnostic and treatment facilities and advanced private clinical services from the centre based at Thorpe Park in Leeds.</p>\r\n<p>Bowman Riley Healthcare was commissioned to design the internal fit out of the new 400m specialist clinic serving NHS and private referral patients.</p>\r\n<p>The stylish, high quality designed interior spaces incorporate a reception, six consulting rooms, treatment room, audiology room, ultrasound and x-ray facilities.</p>\r\n<p>A second phase of the clinic comprising minor operating suite, treatment rooms, five additional consulting rooms, recovery bays, staff accommodation and associated ancillary accommodation.</p>', 'Living Care Group', 'Living Care Group opened a third centre in the Yorkshire region to host a mix of NHS outpatient clinics, extensive diagnostic and treatment facilities and advanced private clinical services from the centre based at Thorpe Park in Leeds.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'living-care-group', '', '', '2014-10-30 11:23:04', '2014-10-30 11:23:04', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=casestudies&#038;p=519', 0, 'casestudies', '', 0),
(520, 1, '2014-10-30 11:23:01', '2014-10-30 11:23:01', '', 'Thorpe-Park-Clinic-1200x800', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'thorpe-park-clinic-1200x800', '', '', '2014-10-30 11:23:01', '2014-10-30 11:23:01', '', 519, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Thorpe-Park-Clinic-1200x800.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(521, 1, '2014-10-30 11:24:50', '2014-10-30 11:24:50', '<h3>Westcliffe Medical Centre</h3>\r\n<p>Westcliffe Medical Centre is a long established Shipley practice, which is part of NHS Bradford and Airedale and Leeds Primary Care Trust cluster. The practice offers high quality care to its patients and as part of its commitment to improving the centre invested in refurbishment works.</p>\r\n<p>Bowman Riley Healthcare was commissioned directly by the practice to provide architecture and project management services for the internal refurbishment of the existing medical centre</p>\r\n<p>The works comprised the refurbishment of the reception and entrance areas and consulting rooms involving new reception desk, floor finishes, IPS panels and decorations.</p>\r\n<p>The project was successfully completed to Care Quality Commission (CQC) standards.</p>', 'Westcliffe Medical Centre', 'Westcliffe Medical Centre is a long established Shipley practice, which is part of NHS Bradford and Airedale and Leeds Primary Care Trust cluster. The practice offers high quality care to its patients and as part of its commitment to improving the centre invested in refurbishment works.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'westcliffe-medical-centre', '', '', '2014-10-30 13:56:10', '2014-10-30 13:56:10', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=casestudies&#038;p=521', 0, 'casestudies', '', 0),
