(529, 1, '2014-10-22 11:31:18', '2014-10-22 11:31:18', '<p>Bowman Riley Architects recently sponsored Skipton golfer, Malcolm Elrick in his bid to retain the European blind golf title.</p>\r\n<p>Malcolm came second in the prestigious European tournament.</p>\r\n<p>Bowman Riley organises a very popular annual golf day at Skipton Golf Club every June for clients, staff and friends of the company. Malcolm will present the winner of the 2015 Bowman Riley Golf Day the companys trophy.</p>\r\n<p>Photo - Malcolm Elrick with Andrea Calcaterra, the tournament organiser and rest of the world captain</p>', 'Sponsoring the European Blind Golf Champion', 'Bowman Riley Architects recently sponsored Skipton golfer, Malcolm Elrick in his bid to retain the European blind golf title.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'sponsoring-european-blind-golf-champion', '', '', '2014-10-30 11:32:34', '2014-10-30 11:32:34', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=news&#038;p=529', 0, 'news', '', 0),
