(533, 1, '2014-10-24 11:36:08', '2014-10-24 11:36:08', '<p>For the fifth consecutive year, Bowman Riley Architects has been selected as one of the top 50 companies to work for in the UKs construction industry by Building magazine as featured in this month''s Good Employer Guide.</p>\r\n<p>Companies included in the guide stand out because of the benefits they offer their staff, ranging from training opportunities to career progression and a healthy work-life balance.</p>\r\n<p>Bowman Riley Architects recognises that investment in our people in terms of career development, staff satisfaction and a rewarding work environment is critical to the success of our business.</p>', 'Building Good Employer Guide 2014', 'For the fifth consecutive year, Bowman Riley Architects has been selected as one of the top 50 companies to work for in the UKs construction industry by Building magazine as featured in this month''s Good Employer Guide.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'building-good-employer-guide-2014', '', '', '2014-10-30 11:36:40', '2014-10-30 11:36:40', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=news&#038;p=533', 0, 'news', '', 0),
