(538, 1, '2014-10-30 12:10:28', '2014-10-30 12:10:28', '<h3>Bupa Cromwell Hospital</h3>\r\n<p>Bowman Riley Architects was commissioned to design the internal refurbishment of four floors of Bupa Cromwell Hospital, a renowned private hospital, based in central London, which opened in 1981 as a state-of-the-art private facility for complex medical procedures.</p>\r\n<p>To enhance the hospitals reputation for excellence in patient care, Bupa needed to refurbish ward accommodation, consulting rooms, paediatric and ancillary accommodation to comply with the current best practice guidance on the design of healthcare facilities; Health Technical Memoranda (HTMs) and Health Building Notes (HBN).</p>\r\n<p>Working with the main contractor, Bowman Riley is currently producing construction information to tight deadlines whilst the hospital is fully operational.</p>', 'Bradford NHS Foundation Trust', 'Bowman Riley Architects was commissioned to design the internal refurbishment of four floors of Bupa Cromwell Hospital, a renowned private hospital, based in central London, which opened in 1981 as a state-of-the-art private facility for complex medical procedures.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bupa', '', '', '2014-10-30 12:56:25', '2014-10-30 12:56:25', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=casestudies&#038;p=538', 0, 'casestudies', '', 0),
