(565, 1, '2014-10-30 15:02:23', '2014-10-30 15:02:23', '<h1>Innovate</h1>\r\n<p>Bowman Riley Innovate was formed in 2012 to explore and discover new ways of interacting with the built environment, with a view to offering added value to our clients in this rapidly changing technological age.</p>\r\n<p>Our team acts as an incubator for commercially viable and tangible ideas that deliver creative solutions through products, processes and software that enable our clients to get greater flexibility, value and use from their assets.</p>\r\n<p>A specific product we have taken to market is a modular IPS doorset unit, which has been designed in a unique way to prevent bio-contamination and help in the fight against infection control, and for ease of maintenance in healthcare environments.</p>\r\n<p>Our culture of collaborative working and holistic thinking with clients, academia and partners worldwide has led to the development of other exciting products and innovations to take to market in the near future. For further details contact info@bowmanriley.com.</p>', 'Innovate', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '247-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-30 15:02:23', '2014-10-30 15:02:23', '', 247, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/uncategorized/247-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
