(595, 1, '2014-11-04 09:20:22', '2014-11-04 09:20:22', '<h1>Coordinated<br /><em>Consultancy</em></h1>\r\n<p>We provide high quality coordinated project, management and property consultancy services that support our clients in achieving their built environment aspirations on new projects, refurbishment schemes and estates rationalisation.</p>\r\n<p>Our tailored solutions are applied with ingenuity through our main services:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Building Surveying</li>\r\n<li>Project Management</li>\r\n<li>Cost Consultancy</li>\r\n<li>Health &amp; Safety</li>\r\n<li>Sustainability</li>\r\n<li>Estate and Facilities Consultancy</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Building Consultancy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '20-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-04 09:20:22', '2014-11-04 09:20:22', '', 20, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/uncategorized/20-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(596, 1, '2014-11-04 09:22:54', '2014-11-04 09:22:54', '<h1>Designing for change in<br /><em>Healthcare</em></h1>\r\n<p>Bowman Riley Healthcare Architects design high quality healthcare and social care environments that enhance the patient journey and focus on improved health outcomes.</p>\r\n<p>Designing new buildings, re-configuring existing properties and rationalising healthcare estates, the team provides solutions to the 21st century challenges of increasing efficiency, achieving cost savings and addressing the evolving clinical and patients needs.</p>\r\n<p>Working in collaboration with healthcare clients, government bodies, community healthcare partnerships, providers of aged and dementia care, academic institutions and leading industry professionals, we are at the forefront of healthcare design and innovation. Our team co-founded the Health BIM group working alongside the Department of Health, NHS and private sector partners on the Integrated Health Information Model.</p>\r\n<p>As a joint venture partner with TAHPI, we are the European partners of the Health Facility Briefing System, a web suite of integrated tools offered on a subscription basis to support the health industry.</p>', 'Healthcare', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '22-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-04 09:22:54', '2014-11-04 09:22:54', '', 22, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/uncategorized/22-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(597, 1, '2014-11-04 10:03:56', '2014-11-04 10:03:56', '<h1>DELIVERING THOUGHTFUL &amp; RESPONSIVE DESIGN SINCE 1968</h1>\r\n<p>Bowman Riley provides innovative architecture and integrated building consultancy operating across the UK.</p>With over 45 years experience, our award winning team of 70 continues to successfully deliver a range of projects that transform our clients visions into reality.</p>Our approach is to combine design excellence with practical expertise founded on solid commercial knowledge that ensures our projects are both realistic and achievable.</p>', 'All About Bowman Riley', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-04 10:03:56', '2014-11-04 10:03:56', '', 2, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/uncategorized/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
