(606, 1, '2014-11-04 10:55:21', '2014-11-04 10:55:21', '<h1>Building Surveying</h1>\r\n<p>Our building surveying team is experienced in looking after wide range of buildings to support owners, occupiers and investors with the purchase, maintenance, management, rationalisation, enhancement and disposal of their built assets. </p>\r\n<p>Lead by RICS chartered building surveyors our team includes cost, access, sustainability, structural and building services consultants. This allows us to deliver a comprehensive and coordinated range of specialist services across the UK including:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Estate rationalisation surveys / multi facet surveys / property strategies</li>\r\n<li>Building surveys</li>\r\n<li>Design and refurbishment</li>\r\n<li>Rights to light / sunlight daylight assessments</li>\r\n<li>Access consultancy</li>\r\n<li>Dilapidations</li>\r\n<li>Fire risk assessments</li>\r\n<li>Expert witness</li>\r\n<li>Conservation consultancy</li>\r\n<li>Bank fund monitoring</li>\r\n<li>Building cost reinstatement valuation</li>\r\n<li>Cost consultancy</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Building Surveying', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '213-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-04 10:55:21', '2014-11-04 10:55:21', '', 213, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/uncategorized/213-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(607, 1, '2014-11-04 11:02:55', '2014-11-04 11:02:55', '<h1>Your project is in safe hands</h1>\r\n<p>Our team of qualified project managers have wide ranging experience in leading the successful delivery of projects on time, within budget and to the highest of standards.</p>\r\n<p>Our client focused methods are proven, allowing our enthusiastic hands-on professional project managers to motivate the whole team, minimise risks and exceed expectations whilst delivering your projects.</p>\r\n<p>Our services include:</p>\r\n<p>Project Management  Programme management  Employers agent  Contract administration  Risk management  Move management  Feasibility studies / option appraisals / Estate rationalisation  Fund / development monitoring  Technical Advisor  Independent certifier  Full design, management and property consultancy service</p>\r\n<p>Contact: Robin Holme MRICS MAPM<br />07718 523 822<br />robin.holme@bowmanriley.com</p>', 'Project Management', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '215-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-04 11:02:55', '2014-11-04 11:02:55', '', 215, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/uncategorized/215-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
