(612, 1, '2014-11-04 11:39:36', '2014-11-04 11:39:36', '<h1>BIM</h1>\r\n<p>At Bowman Riley we embrace technology and innovation that deliver tangible benefits improve the service we provide our clients. The 21st century has seen unprecedented technological developments and an explosion of data available about the built environment.</p>\r\n<p>One of the most exciting developments to influence the design, construction and management of the built environment is Building Information Modelling (BIM). We see BIM as a catalyst for positive change and a significant shift in the way assets are designed, built and delivered for the client.</p>\r\n<p>BIM allows us as designers to create whole projects in a virtual 3D environment improving visualisations and communications. Used as a collaborative tool, BIM improves the pace of delivery, eliminates inconsistencies and provides greater cost certainties. The BIM is as much about people as it is about technology and processes.</p>\r\n<p>With the growing emphasis on the importance of information, BIM can produce data-rich models that can provide links between the technical, operational and strategic elements of the asset development process and beyond. The benefits of BIM to a client or end user extends to the facilities management and maintenance of a building during its life.</p>\r\n<p>We are passionate advocates of the development and expansion of the BIM process. Our team is fully engaged with the UK BIM4SME group and the newly accredited BIM4Health groups, with the latter developing public and private healthcare initiatives. Evidence-based decision making coupled with open BIM and strategic collaborative arrangements are used to help clients and partners in all aspects of the BIM process.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'BIM', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '344-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-04 11:39:36', '2014-11-04 11:39:36', '', 344, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/uncategorized/344-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(613, 1, '2014-11-04 11:50:28', '2014-11-04 11:50:28', '<h1>DELIVERING THOUGHTFUL &amp; RESPONSIVE DESIGN SINCE 1968</h1>\r\n<p>Bowman Riley provides innovative architecture and integrated building consultancy operating across the UK. With over 45 years experience, our award winning team of 70 continues to successfully deliver a range of projects that transform our clients visions into reality.</p>\r\n<p>Our approach is to combine design excellence with practical expertise founded on solid commercial knowledge that ensures our projects are both realistic and achievable.</p>', 'All About Bowman Riley', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-04 11:50:28', '2014-11-04 11:50:28', '', 2, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/uncategorized/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(614, 1, '2014-11-04 12:57:23', '2014-11-04 12:57:23', '<h1>Making a positive contribution</h1>\r\n<p class="p1">CSR covers all our efforts to make a positive contribution to our clients, partners and suppliers, to the communities in which we work, to the lives of our own people, and to the environment. Our CSR policy addresses key areas of responsibility:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class="p1">To create positive working environments where our people are happy and motivated to be the best they can be</li>\r\n<li class="p1">To undertake business fairly and with integrity</li>\r\n<li class="p1">To contribute positively to the communities in which we work</li>\r\n<li class="p1">To protect the environment</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class="p1">Our people</h3>\r\n<p class="p1">Our success as a company depends on the commitment of our people and on the support that we give them. We continue to:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class="p1">Provide learning and development support</li>\r\n<li class="p1">Improve the well-being of our staff and encourage work/life balance</li>\r\n<li class="p1">Support equality and diversity</li>\r\n<li class="p1">Maintain our Investors in People accreditation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class="p1">Our business</h3>\r\n<p class="p1">We are committed to acting honestly and fairly in all our dealings with our clients, suppliers and partners. We continue to:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class="p1">Improve client feedback results</li>\r\n<li class="p1">Promote anti-bribery and corruption</li>\r\n<li class="p1">Celebrate success and recognise excellence</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class="p1">Our communities</h3>\r\n<p class="p1">We are committed to ensuring that the impact we have on the communities where we live and work is as positive as possible. We continue to:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class="p1">Support a nominated charity of the year</li>\r\n<li class="p1">Increase participation in staff volunteering</li>\r\n<li class="p1">Increase the number of pro bono services for community projects</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class="p1">Our environment</h3>\r\n<p class="p1">We understand the environmental impacts the construction industry has on our world and we are fully committed to promoting sustainable designs and to manage our own workplaces as sustainably as possible. We continue to:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class="p1">Positively influence our clients to improve the sustainability of their projects, estates and operations</li>\r\n<li class="p1">Raise awareness of environmental issues amongst our people</li>\r\n<li class="p1">Reduce our own waste, water consumption and CO2 emissions and increase recycling</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><a href="http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/CSR-logos.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-335" src="http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/CSR-logos.jpg" alt="CSR-logos" width="300" height="70" /></a></p>', 'Our CSR', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '14-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-04 12:57:23', '2014-11-04 12:57:23', '', 14, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/uncategorized/14-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(615, 1, '2014-11-04 14:11:00', '2014-11-04 14:11:00', '<h1>COMMERCIALLY<br />CREATIVE<em>ARCHITECTS</em></h1>\r\n<p>A commitment to high quality and innovative design is at the very heart of the projects we create.</p>\r\n<p>With significant experience in the delivery of a wide range of new and refurbished buildings, we help our clients realise their built environment aspirations.</p>\r\n<p>From small complex projects to multi-million pound developments and roll-out programmes, our team has the practical expertise to take a project from concept planning to completion on site.</p>\r\n<p>Working in partnership with our clients and the wider design and construction team, we strive to lead the way in terms of innovation, efficiency and sustainability to deliver tangible benefits for our clients.</p>\r\n<p>Please explore our services and case studies for more information.</p>', 'Architects', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '18-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-04 14:11:00', '2014-11-04 14:11:00', '', 18, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/uncategorized/18-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
